pgTitle: List of organisms named after famous people

rows.text: Named "in reference to the markedly developed (biceps-like) middle femora of the males of this species reminiscent of the actor's physique."
This fly dies with its midlegs in a bandy-legged position.
A species of weevil named for the author of the Aubrey-Maturin books.
Iago is "James" and badius is "brown" in Latin.

Diapriid wasp described as "a solitary female".
The horse fly was named after the singer and actress because of its striking golden behind.
